# The v2 digest: global standards plus your declared libraries.
Output docs/demos/gif/05-library-digest.gif
Output docs/demos/mp4/05-library-digest.mp4
Source docs/demos/tapes/lib/style.tape
Set Height 880
Source docs/demos/tapes/lib/world.tape

Type "cd ../acme-api"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 700ms

Type "roboto-mem sync"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 1500ms

Type "roboto-mem digest"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 9s
